title: DDFP 380: AFC East 'Jenga' pieces
itunes:title: DDFP 380: AFC East 'Jenga' pieces
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and NFL Fantasy Live's Marcas Grant and Alex Gelhar to break down this season's high-risk and high-reward fantasy players and how Kelvin Benjamin's injury affects the receiver field. Plus, the guys debate which player is the "Jenga" piece for each AFC East team.
